<p>The Teacher is not a production part of your colony, but rather a way to increase the stats of your children. The Teacher will teach the <a href="../workers/pupil">Pupils</a> (children) of the colony to increase their skill levels. While they can teach without supplies, providing paper will increase the speed that the Pupils level.</p>
